- [ ] Identify the build script or build procedure for the APK.
- [ ] Run the web build step (`npm run build`).
- [ ] Sync the web build with Capacitor (`npx cap sync android`).
- [ ] Build the Android APK using Gradle.
- [ ] Move/Rename the APK to `StockFlowAI_Final_v27.apk` in the user's main workspace.
